{"tid":1757691,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[行動]和你lunch 可引入唔同主題，增加曝光率","createTime":"2019-11-26T15:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:19:36.000Z","uid":300294,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"05b2dff2c27cdae08e926c31ac55f0b11b3befbd","tid":1757691,"uid":300294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"首先，見到每日lunch time 咁多手足出黎都好開心，係做到集氣既效果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我覺得和你lunch 其實係好有潛力，去幫示威者做PR野，甚至傳達訊息俾國際社會。畢竟，假日遊行好易俾人清場，跟住傳媒就只係掛住報警民衝突。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一樣我覺得可以做係每日定唔同主題。始終日日都係同一樣野 其實傳媒會覺得無新聞價值去報，同好快悶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而示威者其實有唔同主題可以做，包括<br />\n1. 國際求援 (可以每次唔同國家)<br />\n2. 宣揚中共既事蹟 (人權問題，間諜問題)<br />\n3. 聲討協助逼害香港人既公司或主要人物 (每次唔同公司，例如apple)<br />\n4. 警暴問題<br />\n5. 香港政府其他問題 (大白象工程、貪腐etc)<br />\n<br />\n上述只係幾個例子，而實際操作上每個星期可以用更specific 既題材。例如國際求援上，一個星期講美國，另一星期講英國，再下個星期德國咁樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣就唔會日日做同一樣野，傳媒亦都多d野報。<br />\n我最希望係引到外媒報，咁就同時做到集氣 、PR 同 幫到國際線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然希望大家保持和平理性，並且唔好犯法。一陣警察見到大家犯法，又想傳遞政治敏感既訊息，有可能衝過黎拉人或射TG ，引起大混亂，對大家同其他上班族都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"f987defc5386971a7341b79dc36ef5970bbabddd","tid":1757691,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90056bca7648d0ebb219260419d858b61ce7f630","tid":1757691,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de50204985db394eaba99c8fc6cfa0889558066d","tid":1757691,"uid":195867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"推返d行動post出黎啦"},{"pid":"76d67d46b57fa8dfaf903d48aa62737ce5e78913","tid":1757691,"uid":51757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:55:34.000Z","msg":"Agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日Save PolyU新聞效果都強好多<br />\n有主題比9行更有目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3e96e5ea440bee322c009f6764999c335497d1","tid":1757691,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c8a3a6f733e59f8c03171aeb6612e91e6f5cb4c","tid":1757691,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:20:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e93117224b77388a054d1a2384da9fb55a5d268b","tid":1757691,"uid":338362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b8d1e3fb3f87503ac9d01893a28f6cef0b54c296","tid":1757691,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:11:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14051d74e625e58dfb68ef5f2464db4536040a40","tid":1757691,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"既然啲狗唔放tg唔清場，唔我地就轉型做文宣"},{"pid":"3c0fdc33d1097af93e86147df4ec2c94805d0c84","tid":1757691,"uid":170812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:22:11.000Z","msg":"要啦。<br />\n公司印完文宣就落街食lunch。"},{"pid":"03a1467532e7fb9a43c328de53a5ccf3f5a338d5","tid":1757691,"uid":51757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab277df9c86cb263fa9f01f86253d18e194c79a0","tid":1757691,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"貼文宣呀<br />\n善用公司資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e010878